verview of bright mountain media inc snapshot people company overview bright mountain media inc a media holding company owns and manages websites in the united states it operates through two segments product sales and services the company develops websites which provide information and news to military law enforcement first responders and other public safety employees and information including originally written news content blogs forums career information and videos it sells various products including watches clocks and apparel through its websites ecommerce distributor portals and a retail location the company was formerly known as bright mountain acquisition corporation and changed its name to bright mountain media inc in december bright mountain media inc a media holding company owns and manages websites in the united states it operates through two segments product sales and services the company develops websites which provide information and news to military law enforcement first responders and other public safety employees and information including originally written news content blogs forums career information and videos it sells various products including watches clocks and apparel through its websites ecommerce distributor portals and a retail location the company was formerly known as bright mountain acquisition corporation and changed its name to bright mountain media inc in december  bright mountain media inc was founded in  and is based in boca raton florida detailed description  congress avenuesuite boca raton fl united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwbrightmountainmediacom key executives for bright mountain media inc mr w kip speyer chairman chief executive officer and president age  total annual compensation k mr dennis w healey chief financial officer secretary and director age  total annual compensation k mr jonathan d thielmann general manager of bright watches age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  bright mountain 